	<h1 class="title">The Last of Us 的粉丝就在游戏里当起了导演</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3603/small/3603.png?1414588369" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王杰夫</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-06 08:12:23 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9216/medium/9216.jpg?1436687488" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


